      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ester comprising of heterocyclic moiety, 3-hydroxy-4-{[(6-methoxy-1,3-benzothiazol-2-yl)imino]methyl}phenyl palmitate was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR, elemental analysis and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
